First enable parallel UMC support by defining the number of parallel processes ("0" or "1" ==> only one process):
`ucr set umc/parallel=5`

Start UMC in parallel:
`systemctl restart univention-management-console-web-server-multiprocessing.target`

Restart apache2:
`systemctl restart apache2`

Enable the target if it should start on boot
`systemctl enable univention-management-console-web-server-multiprocessing.target`


Check status of all services in target:
`systemctl list-dependencies univention-management-console-web-server-multiprocessing.target`

To go back to one UMC process, just use:
`ucr unset umc/parallel`
`systemctl stop univention-management-console-web-server-multiprocessing.target`
`systemctl restart apache2`


